My heart breaks for the victims and families affected by today's school shooting in Florida. 

This is the 18th school shooting in the US this year. Once again, our country's gun violence epidemic cries out for action. #EnoughIsEnough
This week @HouseGOP is bringing up a bill that rolls back the Americans with Disabilities Act and sets disability rights back by decades. I oppose attacks on the #ADA — and I will vote NO on #HR620.

I'm heading to Washington now, but @SpeakerRyan only plans 1 full day of work this week — before the House heads out on a 10-day break. 

With so many pressing issues, Congress should be in session. @HouseGOP, it's time to #DoYourJob.
.@realDonaldTrump's #SOTU was long on campaign rhetoric and filled with empty promises of a GOP agenda that continues to divide America.
.@HouseGOP is gearing up to make cuts to Meals on Wheels, Medicaid, nutrition assistance for kids, housing & more. I’m standing with Minnesotans and Americans saying #HandsOff

The President and Congress have just 16 days to reach a long-term budget deal, but @HouseGOP has decided to go home for 6 days instead of negotiating on a budget & other long-term priorities.

Once again, Republicans are completely failing to govern responsibly. #DoYourJob

We all wanted the #TrumpShutdown to end, but the 17-day CR that was passed today does nothing but paper over the abject failure of @realDonaldTrump and @HouseGOP to agree on a budget and address urgent priorities.

I’m a NO vote on the CR that kicks the can down the road for 17 more days. Minnesotans get absolutely nothing from another stopgap with no guarantee of progress on a long-term budget or action on national priorities.

I'm here on the House Floor alongside @HouseDemocrats who are ready to do our work and reach an agreement on the budget & big issues facing our country. 

It's time for @realDonaldTrump & @HouseGOP to stop the political games, negotiate in good faith & end the #TrumpShutdown.
JUST IN: @HouseGOP voted down our effort to ensure that America's men and women in uniform get paid during the #TrumpShutdown. Shameful.

Our country is now just 12 hours from a #GOPshutdown, but @HouseGOP is still planning to adjoun and go home for 9 days. Once again, Republicans are demonstrating a complete failure to govern responsibly. #DoYourJob
The federal government shuts down at midnight, but @HouseGOP is instead spending time on #HR4712. I'm voting NO on this anti-choice bill which puts politicians between physicians & their patients.

BREAKING: With less than 30 hours until a government shutdown, @HouseGOP is now taking a recess to accommodate a Republican political rally in Pennsylvania. Complete failure to govern responsibly. #DoYourJob

Dr. Martin Luther King, Jr. dedicated his life to equality & opportunity for all Americans. He spoke up for civil rights, civil liberties, voting rights, health care, living wages, union representation, women’s reproductive rights & a more peaceful foreign policy. #MLKDay2018
Today we thank the brave women and men in uniform who work hard every day to keep our communities safe. We appreciate all that you do to serve and protect! #LawEnforcementAppreciationDay
Happy 90th Birthday to Vice President Walter Mondale, a tremendous leader for our state and a true Minnesota icon!
After three months wasting time on the #GOPTaxScam, @HouseGOP is now holding government funding hostage to legislation cleaning up some of the cuts the tax bill inflicted on the American people.

.@HouseGOP is voting again on their #GOPTaxScam because they rushed the process & didn’t know what was in their own bill. 

As a reminder, it raises taxes on 86 million middle-class households while cutting taxes for big corporations & billionaires.
BREAKING: @HouseGOP just passed their bill that raises taxes on middle class Minnesotans to pay for a deficit-exploding giveaway to big corporations and billionaires. #GOPTaxScam

Minnesotans have made their voices heard in strong opposition to the #GOPTaxScam. Calls & correspondence to my office:

OPPOSE: 5734 
SUPPORT: 86

I’m heading to the House Floor to vote NO now.

The final version of @HouseGOP's tax bill: 

- still raises taxes on the middle class 
- still kicks 13 million people off their health coverage
- still explodes the deficit. 

I'm still a NO vote on the #GOPTaxScam.
I'm joining @tptAlmanac tonight at 7 p.m. Central to talk about the #GOPTaxScam and the news of the week. Tune in!

As @FCC debates ending #NetNeutrality, @HouseGOP just voted to make it easier for big banks to share customers' personal info without notice. 

It's obvious: Republicans care more about enriching big corporations & billionaires than protecting working families.

Why are @SenateMajLdr & the Republicans rushing to pass their tax bill before @GDouglasJones is seated? 

They're scared that slowing down and being transparent will give Americans time to learn just how bad the #GOPTaxScam really is for our families.

Who are some of the people @HouseGOP's tax bill hits the hardest?

Teachers
… and seniors
… and veterans
… and students
… and ppl w/ disabilities & chronic illnesses

We must stop the #GOPTaxScam.

I voted NO on @SpeakerRyan's plan to kick the can down the road on passing a federal budget. Instead of lurching from crisis to crisis, @HouseGOP should work with us to meet the needs of the American people and fully fund our government for the entire fiscal year.

As we move forward, I know that Governor Mark Dayton will appoint a qualified person to serve Minnesotans in the Senate. I look forward to working with our new Senator to help Minnesota families and stand up to President Trump and the Republicans’ divisive agenda.
Today is a sad day for Minnesota. Senator Al Franken has been more than a colleague — he has been a friend and an ally on the issues that are most important to Minnesota families.

It’s horrifying that @HouseGOP just passed legislation that forces states to let violent offenders, domestic abusers & stalkers carry hidden, loaded handguns. 

To keep our families safe, I voted NO on #HR38. #StopCCR

The allegations against Senator Al Franken make it impossible for him to be an effective Senator for Minnesota. 

When he makes his announcement tomorrow, I have every confidence that he will do the right thing for Minnesota and our country.

Today @HouseGOP will vote on #HR38, legislation that forces states to let violent offenders carry hidden, loaded handguns. I oppose this dangerous bill, which will make our families and communities less safe. #StopCCR

Very disappointed @HouseGOP just voted down @HouseDemocrats motion to save the state and local tax deduction.

It’s sad that Republicans so intent on raising taxes on middle class Minnesotans. #GOPTaxScam

Preserving places like Bears Ears & Grand Staircase-Escalante is the reason Congress passed the Antiquities Act. We must keep working to safeguard our public lands & save America’s treasures. #MonumentsForAll #StandWithBearsEars #SaveGrandStaircase
Congrats to @HAFAfarmers on receiving a $175,000 grant from @usdaRD to support your great work strengthening our communities!

.@SenateGOP just voted down a Democratic attempt to save the state and local tax deduction, which benefits hundreds of thousands of middle class Minnesotans.

Repealing SALT is yet another way the #GOPTaxScam hurts people in MN and across America.

Who will be hurt by the #GOPTaxScam?
→ Students
→ Teachers
→ Veterans
→ Seniors
→ People with disabilities
→ Homeowners
→ First responders
→ People with chronic illnesses

H.R. 3905 shortcircuits a careful environmental review and fundamentally alters federal environmental protections to benefit a Chilean mining conglomerate with a poor environmental record. 

To #SaveTheBWCA, we must defeat this dangerous bill.

The U.S. House will vote today on H.R. 3905, which paves the way for dangerous sulfide-ore copper mining on the doorstep of the Boundary Waters. 

I'm urging my colleagues to join me and vote NO on this dangerous bill. We must #SaveTheBWCA.

The Fond du Lac, Grand Portage, and White Earth Bands of Minnesota Chippewa all oppose dangerous sulfide-ore copper mining adjacent to the #BWCA. 

That's one reason I'm fighting to stop H.R. 3905. #SaveTheBWCA
Thank you to my Minnesota colleagues @keithellison and @RepErikPaulsen for speaking out today against H.R. 3905. People of both parties know we must #SaveTheBWCA!

Today the House is considering a destructive bill that paves the way for dangerous sulfide-ore copper mining on the doorstep of the Boundary Waters. 

We must #SaveTheBWCA and stop H.R. 3905.

I'm heading to the House Floor now to speak against H.R. 3115, which undermines due process, environmental safeguards & the treaty rights of Native Americans, all to expedite construction of the Polymet mine.

Navajo code talkers are heroes who deserve to be honored at the White House. But @realDonaldTrump’s remarks today disparaged Native Americans & demeaned the Presidency.  

It is truly sad that the President can’t honor our heroes without being disrespectful & divisive.
I’m joining @Ali_Lucia on @WCCO at 10:30 AM to talk about my recent Congressional delegation to Burma and Bangladesh, the harmful #GOPTaxScam & other news of the day. Tune in!
Today is #SmallBizSaturday! Support small, locally-owned businesses and #ShopSmall today! cc: @MetroIBA

The allegations against Senator Franken are very disturbing. The account and the photo released today can only be described as completely inappropriate. 

The Senate Ethics Committee should conduct a formal investigation.
FACT CHECK on #GOPTaxScam: cutting taxes on the wealthiest Americans and adding $1.5 trillion dollars to the deficit means America’s middle class and children are left with the bill.
Get to know the #GOPTaxScam bill on the Floor today — @HouseGOP will raise taxes on middle-class families, cut taxes for the wealthy & add $1.5 trillion dollars to the deficit.
We need a tax plan where corporations and the wealthiest pay their fair share. Not one that burdens middle class families and takes away health care from millions. #GOPTaxScam
RT if you agree that middle class families shouldn’t suffer while the millionaires & billionaires are given a tax break. #GOPTaxScam
.@AARP, @NCPSSM, @CMAorg, @justiceinaging, @EldercareTeam all oppose @HouseGOP’s tax bill. We must stop this attack on older Americans. #GOPTaxScam

text: Republicans are exploding the deficit w/their #GOPTaxScam, all so they can turn around and cut #Medicare. American seniors don’t deserve to foot the bill so billionaires and corporations get a tax break.

The Work Opportunity Tax Credit helps employers hire new employees and create jobs. It’s appalling that @HouseGOP’s tax bill completely erases this tax credit. #GOPTaxScam

Tomorrow, @HouseGOP will bring up their tax bill to the House Floor. This bill raises taxes on middle class Minnesotans, while cutting taxes for big corporations and billionaires. 

I am a strong NO vote on the #GOPTaxScam.
